outputs.output_descr:
The main strategy of this short term project will be providing continuity of project activities that have been initiated within SCIBM project as well as working with the government of Azerbaijan on preparation of immediate implementations of new project on IBM introduction at the green border intersection between Azerbaijan and Georgia, when funding for the new project is available.

Specific goals of this short-term project will include: 
-	
-	Monitoring of implementations of decisions that have been taken over implementation of SCIBM project;
-	Followup on activities that have been initiated during last phase of the SCIBM project implementation;
-	Follow-up on timely submission and approval of new AZE-GEO project to be submitted to EU for funding;
-	Preparatory work for the immediate start of implementations of the new project when funding is confirmed
-	Continued collaboration with national partner on development of new project proposals
